<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Anime Night Club - Registrazione</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        body { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; }
        .auth-container { 
            background: var(--bg-panel); 
            padding: 40px; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            border: 1px solid var(--neon-pink); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-pink); 
            text-align: center; 
            width: 100%; 
            max-width: 400px; 
        }
        .auth-container h1 { color: var(--neon-pink); margin-bottom: 20px; text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-pink); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="dark-theme">
    <div class="auth-container">
        <h1>REGISTRAZIONE</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--neon-yellow);">
            Il primo utente registrato diventerà automaticamente l'Owner!
        </p>
        <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Scegli un Username" required>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Scegli una Password" required>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Registrati</button>
        </form>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            Hai già un account? <a href="/login" style="color: var(--neon-cyan);">Fai Login</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>